platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: From the second Barry Steakfries busts through that laboratory wall, Jetpack Joyride thrusts you into an unforgettable horizontal adventure. This stylish infinite runner gets your pulse pounding as you feverishly snag coins, dodge obstacles and take rides in crazy vehicles (think: robotic dragons and money-propelled birds). Its a classic thats only gotten better over the years, thanks to Halfbrick Studios' consistent updates.
